\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n\r\n                <div class=\"col-md-7 col-xs-12\">\r\n\r\n                    <ul class=\"imagine-list\">\r\n                        <li class=\"wow fadeIn\" data-wow-delay=\"0.2s\"><h3>Customer Engagement</h3>\r\n                            <p>Enhance customer engagement with our cutting-edge chatbot solutions. Our AI-powered\r\n                                chatbots provide personalized interactions, timely assistance, and seamless\r\n                                communication, driving customer satisfaction and loyalty.</p>\r\n                        </li>\r\n                        <li class=\"wow fadeIn\" data-wow-delay=\"0.4s\"><h3>Automation with bots</h3>\r\n                            <p>Streamline workflows and boost productivity with our automation bots. AI-driven\r\n                                bots automate repetitive tasks, accelerate processes, and improve efficiency across\r\n                                organizations. From data entry and document processing to customer service and support,\r\n                                our bots optimize operations, saving time and resources while enhancing overall\r\n                                performance.</p>\r\n                        </li>\r\n                        <li class=\"wow fadeIn\" data-wow-delay=\"0.6s\"><h3>Scalability</h3>\r\n                            <p>Bots that serve as powerful assets for customer interaction. Bots are\r\n                                designed to be intuitive, responsive, and capable of providing personalized experiences,\r\n                                nurturing enduring customer connections.</p>\r\n                        </li>\r\n                        <li class=\"wow fadeIn\" data-wow-delay=\"0.8s\"><h3>Tailored Solutions</h3>\r\n                            <p>Recognizing the distinctiveness of each business, our skilled professionals carefully\r\n                                develop c