ay\" role=\"img\">\r\n\r\n                </svg>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <script>\r\n                var promise = document.querySelector('#video-container video').play();\r\n\r\n                function playVideo() {\r\n                    var video = document.querySelector('#video-container video');\r\n                    video.play();\r\n                    document.querySelector('.play-button').style.display = 'none';\r\n                }\r\n\r\n                if (promise !== undefined) {\r\n                    promise.then(_ => {\r\n                        // Autoplay started!\r\n                    }).catch(error => {\r\n                        document.querySelector('.play-button').style.display = 'block';\r\n                        // Autoplay was prevented.\r\n                        // Show a \"Play\" button so that user can start playback.\r\n                    });\r\n                }\r\n            </script>\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n        <div class=\"container\">\r\n            <div class=\"row\">\r\n                <div class=\"col-md-offset-1 col-md-10 col-xs-12\">\r\n                    <div class=\"content wow fadeInUp\">\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </section>\r\n\r\n    <section class=\"technology-partnership\">\r\n        <div class=\"container\" style=\"position: relative\">\r\n            <div class=\"title-wrap\">\r\n                <h2 class=\"h3 section__title wow fadeInUp\">Popular providers for your success</h2></div>\r\n            <div class=\"items\">\r\n                <a class=\"block-link item wow fadeInUp\" data-wow-delay=\"0s\"\r\n                   target=\"\">\r\n                    <div class=\"icon\">\r\n                        <img alt=\"Meta logo\"\r\n                             class=\"lazy loaded\"\r\n                             data-src=\"https://soutsob.com/resources/img/backend/java.png\"\r\n                             data-was-processed=\"true\" height=\"45\" src=\"https://soutsob.com/resources/img/backend/java.png\" width=\"80\">\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class=\"title\">Java</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"description\"><p>Java is a high-level, object-oriented programming language known for its\r\n                        platform independence, achieved through the Java Virtual Machine (JVM).\r\n                        It is widely used for building secure, robust, and scalable applications, ranging from web and\r\n                        mobile apps to enterprise and embedded systems.\r\n                        Java emphasizes simplicity, portability, and performance, supported by a vast ecosystem of\r\n                        libraries and frameworks.\r\n                        Its \"write once, run anywhere\" philosophy makes it a preferred choice for developers building\r\n                        cross-platform solutions.</p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </a>\r\n                <div class=\"block-link item wow fadeInUp\" data-wow-delay=\"0.1s\">\r\n                    <div class=\"icon\">\r\n                        <img alt=\"Meta logo\"\r\n                             class=\"lazy loaded\"\r\n                             data-src=\"https://soutsob.com/resources/img/backend/nodejs.png\"\r\n                             data-was-processed=\"true\" height=\"45\" src=\"https://soutsob.com/resources/img/backend/nodejs.png\" width=\"80\">\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class=\"title\">Node.js</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"description\"><p>Node.js is a runtime environment that enables developers to run\r\n                        JavaScript on the server side, beyond the browser.\r\n                        Built on Chrome's JavaScript engine, it offers high performance and event-driven, non-blocking\r\n                        I/O, making it ideal for real-time applications and scalable network solutions.\r\n                        Its ecosystem, powered by npm (Node Package Manager), provides access to numerous modules for\r\n                        fast development.\r\n                        Node.js is particularly suited for creating APIs, microservices, and streaming services,\r\n                        supporting asynchronous programming for efficient resource use.</p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"block-link item wow fadeInUp\" data-wow-delay=\"0.2s\">\r\n                    <div class=\"icon\">\r\n                        <img alt=\"Meta logo\"\r\n                             class=\"lazy loaded\"\r\n                             data-src=\"https://soutsob.com/resources/img/backend/python.png\"\r\n                             data-was-processed=\"true\" height=\"45\" src=\"https://soutsob.com/resources/img/backend/python.png\" width=\"80\">\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class=\"title\">Python</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"description\"><p>Python is a versatile, high-level programming language known for its\r\n                        simplicity and readability.\r\n                        It supports multiple programming paradigms, including object-oriented, procedural, and\r\n                        functional programming.\r\n                        Python is widely used in web development, data analysis, artificial intelligence, machine\r\n                        learning, and scripting.\r\n                        Its extensive standard library and community-contributed packages make it a powerful tool for\r\n                        rapid development.\r\n                        With frameworks like Django and Flask, it’s a popular choice for backend development, while\r\n                        libraries like Pandas and TensorFlow cater to data and AI-related tasks.\r\n                        Python's ease of learning makes it beginner-friendly yet powerful for professionals.</p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </section>\r\n\r\n    <section class=\"cta\">\r\n        <div class=\"container\">\r\n            <div class=\"row\">\r\n                <div class=\"col-sm-7 col-xs-12\">\r\n                    <div class=\"form-wrap\">\r\n                        <div class=\"title\">How To Find Us</div>\r\n                        <p class=\"subtitle\">Ask Us Anything.</p>\r\n\r\n                        <div class=\"wpcf7 no-js\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"wpcf7-f5-o1\" lang=\"en-US\">\r\n                            <div class=\"screen-reader-response\"><p aria-atomic=\"true\" aria-live=\"polite\"\r\n                                                                   role=\"status\"></p>\r\n                                <ul></ul>\r\n                            </div>\r\n\r\n                            <form action=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/u/3/d/e/1FAIpQLSfAt8tCKdosqiBZQV0jTX_89qfRg8mCPzW3kghk_YgpWjWVbQ/formResponse\"\r\n                                  data-clean-viewform-url=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfAt8tCKdosqiBZQV0jTX_89qfRg8mCPzW3kghk_YgpWjWVbQ/viewform\" data-dlp-data=\"%.@.null,false]\" data-first-entry=\"0\" data-is-first-page=\"true\"\r\n                                  data-last-entry=\"4\"\r\n                                  data-response=\"%.@.]\"\r\n                                  data-shuffle-seed=\"-7404545974625691574\" id=\"mG61Hd\" jsmodel=\"TOfxwf Q91hve CEkLOc\"\r\n                                  method=\"POST\" onsubmit=\"submitted=true;\" target=\"iframe\">\r\n\r\n                                <div style=\"display: none;\">\r\n                                    <input name=\"_wpcf7\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"5\"/>\r\n                                    <input name=\"_wpcf7_version\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"5.8.7\"/>\r\n                                    <input name=\"_wpcf7_locale\" type=\"hidden\" value