ght: 18px\r\n            }\r\n\r\n            .breadcrumblist .separator {\r\n                font-size: 18px;\r\n                padding: 0 8px;\r\n            }\r\n\r\n            .breadcrumblist > :first-child {\r\n                color: #454545\r\n            }</style>\r\n            <div class=\"breadcrumblist\">\r\n                <a href=\"https://soutsob.com/\">soutsob</a><span class=\"separator\"><svg fill=\"none\" height=\"10\"\r\n                                                                                          width=\"6\"><path\r\n                    d=\"m1 1 3.9 3.9V5L1 9\" stroke=\"#787878\"/></svg></span><span class=\"last-item\">Cookie Policy</span>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class=\"container content\">\r\n            <div class=\"row content-inner\">\r\n                <div class=\"col-lg-9 col-md-10 col-xs-12\">\r\n                    <h1 class=\"h2 article__title\">Cookie Policy</h1>\r\n                </div>\r\n\r\n                <div class=\"col-xs-12\"><h2 class=\"h5-b a-subtitle\">We improve your online experience with cookies</h2>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </section>\r\n\r\n    <div class=\"blog-container container\">\r\n        <article class=\"article blog-article text-block post-15888 page type-page status-publish has-post-thumbnail hentry\"\r\n                 id=\"post-15888\">\r\n            <p>\r\n            <h2>Terms &amp; Conditions</h2>\r\n            <p>\r\n                Our dedication lies in enhancing the user browsing experience and maintaining transparency in our\r\n                approach to collecting and processing user data when accessing our website at <a\r\n                    href=\"https://soutsob.com/\"\r\n                    rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\r\n                    target=\"_blank\">https://soutsob.com/</a>\r\n                (referred to as \"the website\"). This Cookie Policy elaborates on the nature of cookies and the\r\n                utilization of the information received.\r\n                website (hereinafter “the website”).</p>\r\n            <h2>Who are we?</h2>\r\n            <p>TzOV IIT soutsob (\"us\", \"we\", \"our\", or \"soutsob\") established this website to engage with casual\r\n                visitors, potential clients, and businesses interested in our services, while also offering insights\r\n                into soutsob and the IT outsourcing sector. We encourage visitors to freely explore the information\r\n                provided on our website and to utilize the platform to directly connect with SOUTSOB.</p>\r\n            <p>We aim for our website to provide information in a personalized and user-friendly manner, and cookies\r\n                play a role in helping us achieve this objective.</p>\r\n            <p>Upon visiting the website, you will encounter a notification seeking your consent for the use of cookies\r\n                as outlined in this Policy. You have the option to agree to these cookies or adjust your personal\r\n                browser settings. Please note that declining the notification may result in the website not functioning\r\n                correctly.</p>\r\n            <h2>What are cookies?</h2>\r\n            <p>Cookies are tiny snippets of text stored on your device when you browse a website. When you revisit the\r\n                website, the information stored in the cookie is sent back to the site, enabling it to recognize you and\r\n                customize its content to suit your preferences.</p>\r\n            <p>SOUTSOB website uses different types of cookies:</p>\r\n            <ul>\r\n                <li><strong>Session cookies are temporary.</strong> Once the user leaves the website, these cookies\r\n                    automatically expire. Session cookies typically originate from the first-party and are essential for\r\n                    the proper functioning of the website.\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li><strong>Persistent cookies</strong> persist on your device and have a specific expiration date.\r\n                    These cookies may be set by the website or by third parties involved in the operation of the\r\n                    website.\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li><strong>First-party cookies</strong>belong to our website and enable the retention of previous\r\n                    actions and user data preferences.\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li><strong>Third-party cookies</strong> are placed on the user's device by third parties via our\r\n                    website, facilitating the provision of third-party features or functionality on or through the\r\n                    website (such as reporting usage statistics or delivering advertisements).\r\n                </li>\r\n            </ul>\r\n            <p>The first-party and third-party cookies have a wide range of purposes, the main ones are described\r\n                below.</p>\r\n            <p><strong>Essential</strong> or <strong>strictly necessary cookies</strong> serve as a fundamental aspect\r\n                of the website's memory, preserving preferences chosen by users on a specific site, thereby enabling the\r\n                utilization of certain features, such as accessing secure areas of the website.</p>\r\n            <p><strong>Performance cookies</strong> data regarding visitors' interactions with the website, such as the\r\n                most frequently visited pages or occurrences of error messages. These cookies do not collect information\r\n                that personally identifies a visitor; instead, they provide anonymous data that aids in enhancing the\r\n                browsing experience.</p>\r\n            <p><strong>Functionality cookies</strong> enable the website to recall the selections you make, such as user\r\n                name, language, or region, and offer improved, personalized features. Functionality cookies are utilized\r\n                to retain modifications made to customizable sections of web pages. Information received from cookies\r\n                may be anonymized, and browsing activity on other websites cannot be tracked.</p>\r\n            <p><strong>Targeting</strong> or <strong>advertising cookies</strong> are employed to deliver advertising\r\n                that is more tailored to your interests, as well as to restrict the frequency of advertisements you\r\n                encounter and gauge the efficacy of advertising campaigns. Typically placed by advertising networks with\r\n                our consent, these cookies remember your visits to a website and share this information with third\r\n                parties. Often, targeting or advertising cookies are associated with the site functionality offered by\r\n                these third parties.</p>\r\n            <h2>Why does soutsob use cookies?</h2>\r\n            <p>Upon accessing the website, several cookie files are deposited into your web browser. This data can be\r\n                utilized to:</p>\r\n            <ul>\r\n                <li>Activate website functionality and experiment with new pages and features, with the goal of\r\n                    assessing user responses to them.\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li>Process analytical data and track information on how the website is used, so that we can make\r\n                    improvements.\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li>Examine the website to understand users' preferences and actions, identifying any alterations that\r\n                    influence the website's behavior or interface.\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li>Gather data about your activities on the website to deliver pertinent advertisements on our site as\r\n                    well as others.\r\n                </li>\r\n            </ul>\r\n            <p>The information gathered via cookies, which may be installed on your device, will be retained only for\r\n                the duration necessary to fulfill the aforementioned purposes.</p>\r\n            <h2>What are your choices regarding cookies?</h2>\r\n            <p>If you&#8217;d like to delete cookies or instruct your web browser to delete or refuse cookies, please\r\n                visit the help pages of your web browser.</p>\r\n            <p>Please be aware that deleting cookies or declining their acceptance may result in the inability to\r\n                utilize all the features we provide, the inability to store your preferences, and potential display\r\n                issues with some of our pages.</p>\r\n            <ul>\r\n                <li>For the Chrome web browser, please visit this page from Google:<br/>\r\n                    &lt;<a href=\"https://support.google.com/accounts/answer/32050\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\r\n                           target=\"_blank\">https://support.google.com/accounts/answer/32050</a>&gt;\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li>For the Internet Explorer web browser, please visit this page from<br/>\r\n                    Microsoft: &lt;<a href=\"http://support.microsoft.com/kb/278835\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\r\n                                      target=\"_blank\">http://support.microsoft.com/kb/278835</a>&gt;\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li>For the Firefox web browser, please visit this page from Mozilla:<br/>\r\n                    &lt;<a href=\"https://support.mozilla.org/en-US/kb/delete-cookies-remove-info-websites-stored\"\r\n                           rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">https://support.mozilla.org/en-US/kb/delete-cookies-remove-info-websites-stored</a>&gt;\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li>For the Safari web browser, please visit this page from Apple:<br/>\r\n                    &lt;<a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/safari/manage-cookies-and-website-data-sfri11471/mac\"\r\n                           rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">https://support.apple.com/guide/safari/manage-cookies-and-website-data-sfri11471/mac</a>&gt;\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li>For any other web browser, please visit your web browser official web pages.</li>\r\n            </ul>\r\n            <h2>Detailed information about cookies</h2>\r\n            <p>You can learn more about cookies and third-party websites by following these links:</p>\r\n            <ul>\r\n                <li>All About Cookies: <a href=\"http://www.allaboutcookies.org/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\r\n                                          target=\"_blank\">http://www.allaboutcookies.org/</a></li>\r\n                <li>Network Advertising Initiative: <a href=\"http://www.networkadvertising.org/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\r\n                                                       target=\"_blank\">http://www.networkadvertising.org/</a>\r\n                </li>\r\n            </ul>\r\n            <p>If you want to exercise your rights, please contact us.</p>\r\n            <h2>Contact details</h2>\r\n            <p>If you have any inquiries or feedback concerning this Cookie Policy, please feel free to reach out via\r\n                email at <a\r\n                        href=\"https://soutsob.com/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection.html#81f1f3e8f7e0e2f8c1e8eff5e4edede8e0f2afe2eeec\"\r\n                        rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span\r\n                        class=\"__cf_email__\">soutsob@gmail.com</span></a>\r\n                with the subject line “Cookie Policy Request”.</p>\r\n            <p><em>Effective: April 26, 2025</em></p>\r\n\r\n        </article>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <footer class=\"footer\">\r\n        <div class=\"container\">\r\n            <div class=\"row footer__row\">\r\n                <div class=\"col-xs-12 col-md-9 col-sm-8 footer-locations\">\r\n                    <div class=\"footer-logo-wrap\">\r\n       