dev/pwa.png\"\r\n                             data-was-processed=\"true\" height=\"45\" src=\"https://soutsob.com/resources/img/webdev/pwa.png\" width=\"80\">\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class=\"title\">PWA</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"description\"><p>PWA, or Progressive Web App, combines the best features of web and\r\n                        mobile applications to deliver fast, reliable, and engaging user experiences. With PWA, users\r\n                        can access website seamlessly across devices, enjoy offline capabilities, receive push\r\n                        notifications, and experience app-like interactions, all while benefiting from improved\r\n                        performance and discoverability.</p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"block-link item wow fadeInUp\" data-wow-delay=\"0.2s\">\r\n                    <div class=\"icon\">\r\n                        <img alt=\"Meta logo\"\r\n                             class=\"lazy loaded\"\r\n                             data-src=\"https://soutsob.com/resources/img/promotions/googleanalytics.png\"\r\n                             data-was-processed=\"true\" height=\"45\" src=\"https://soutsob.com/resources/img/promotions/googleanalytics.png\" width=\"80\">\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class=\"title\">Google Analytics</div>\r\n                    <div class=\"description\"><p>Google Analytics is a robust web analytics platform that provides\r\n                        valuable insights into website traffic, user behavior, and conversion data. With powerful\r\n                        reporting features and user-friendly dashboards, Google Analytics helps businesses track and\r\n                        analyze their online performance to make data-driven decisions and optimize their digital\r\n                        marketing strategies.</p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n    